title: FS2004 - Santos Dumont Airport+Updade+Serial.
description:
TropicalSim has just released it&#039;s latest scenery. This time it&#039;s one of Brazil&#039;s most charming airports, as well as the fact that it has one of the most difficult approaches in the world, due to all the water sorrounding the airport as well as the Sugar Loaf right on the approach path. The airport has been represented with it&#039;s new passenger terminal, active jetways as well as the other airport buildings carefully defailted in 3d. The airport&#039;s ground also represent the new layout. 

GOOD Flights!!!!
